title: Vote for Influencer Program
body:
This will serve as an outline for a regular reward system to Individuals labelled “Influencers” within our community. These individuals will be decided by the Ambassador Community. This is to reward those who have supported/will support Sarcophagus and it’s community, making an impact in a positive manner in doing so (on a notably larger scale in respect). This program will be approved monthly, and may be ended at any time, if it is deemed best for the community. 
All funds will come from the Ambassador Vault
